column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: TRIDENT GUM STRAWBERRY, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210059451
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

INGREDIENTS: Sweeteners (sorbitol, isomalt, maltitol syrup, maltitol, aspartame, acesulfame K), gum base, acids (E 330, E 296, E 334), thickener (E 414), humectants (E 1518, E 422), flavourings, emulsifier (sunflower lecithin), colours (E 171, E 163), glazing agent (E 903), antioxidant (E 321). Contains a source of phenylalanine. Excess consumption may have a laxative effect.. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 07/25/2016
